display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> into <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[k]]></fr:tex> parts by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[p_k(n)]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p><fr:p>There is no convenient formula for the number <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[p_k(n)]]></fr:tex>, but we have the following recursive formula:
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[     p_k(n) = p_{k - 1}(n - 1) + p_k(n - k)   ]]></fr:tex>
  <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[     p_k(n) = 0 \quad  \text {if} \quad  k > n   ]]></fr:tex></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:p><fr:strong>Labelled Balls, Labelled Boxes</fr:strong>
  <fr:ul><fr:li>unrestricted: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[m^n]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>as least 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[m!S(n, m)]]></fr:tex>, where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[S(n, m)]]></fr:tex> is the Stirling number of the second kind</fr:li>
    <fr:li>at most 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[m^{\underline {n}} = m(m - 1) \cdots  (m - n + 1)]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p><fr:p><fr:strong>Unlabelled Balls, Labelled Boxes</fr:strong>
  <fr:ul><fr:li>unrestricted: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\binom {n + m - 1}{n}]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at least 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\binom {n - 1}{m - 1}]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at most 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\binom {m}{n}]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p><fr:p><fr:strong>Labelled Balls, Unlabelled Boxes</fr:strong>
  <fr:ul><fr:li>unrestricted: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sum _{i = 1}^{m} S(n, i)]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at least 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[S(n, m)]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at most 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[n \leq  m]]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p><fr:p><fr:strong>Unlabelled Balls, Unlabelled Boxes</fr:strong>
  <fr:ul><fr:li>unrestricted: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\sum _{i = 1}^{m} p_i(n)]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at least 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[p_m(n)]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
    <fr:li>at most 1 ball in each box: <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[[n \leq  m]]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:backmatter></fr:tree>